---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Terms of Service"
  description="Terms of Service for Chiltern Computers - Computer repair and IT support services in Harold Hill, Romford, Essex."
>
  <div class="section-bg-1" style="padding: 120px 20px 80px; min-height: 100vh;">
    <div class="container">
      
      <!-- Page Header -->
      <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 60px;">
        <h1 class="space-font galaxy-text cosmic-glow" style="font-size: clamp(32px, 6vw, 48px); margin-bottom: 16px;">
          Terms of Service
        </h1>
        <div style="height: 3px; width: 120px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--plasma-cyan), var(--aurora-green)); margin: 0 auto 20px; border-radius: 2px;"></div>
        <p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--comet-silver); font-size: 16px; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">
          Last updated: January 2025
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Terms Content -->
      <div class="cosmic-card" style="padding: 40px; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
        
        <div class="terms-section">
          <h2 class="space-font" style="color: var(--aurora-green); font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px;">1. Services</h2>
          <p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--starlight-white); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 20px;">
            Chiltern Computers provides computer repair, IT support, custom PC builds, and related technology services. All services are subject to availability and our technical capabilities.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="terms-section">
          <h2 class="space-font" style="color: var(--aurora-green); font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px;">2. Estimates and Pricing</h2>
          <p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--starlight-white); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 20px;">
            All estimates are provided in good faith based on initial diagnosis. Final costs may vary if additional issues are discovered during repair. We will contact you before proceeding with any work that exceeds the original estimate.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="terms-section">
          <h2 class="space-font" style="color: var(--aurora-green); font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px;">3. Warranty</h2>
          <p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--starlight-white); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 20px;">
            We provide a 30-day warranty on repair work performed. This warranty covers the specific repair carried out and does not extend to other components or pre-existing issues. Custom builds include manufacturer warranties on individual components.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="terms-section">
          <h2 class="space-font" style="color: var(--aurora-green); font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px;">4. Data and Privacy</h2>
          <p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--starlight-white); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 20px;">
            While we take reasonable precautions to protect your data, we recommend backing up important files before any repair work. Chiltern Computers is not responsible for data loss during repairs. We do not access, copy, or retain personal data unless required for diagnostic purposes.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="terms-section">
          <h2 class="space-font" style="color: var(--aurora-green); font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px;">5. Liability</h2>
          <p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--starlight-white); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 20px;">
            Our liability is limited to the cost of the repair or service provided. We are not liable for consequential damages, lost profits, or data loss beyond the direct cost of our services.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="terms-section">
          <h2 class="space-font" style="color: var(--aurora-green); font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px;">6. Payment Terms</h2>
          <p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--starlight-white); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 20px;">
            Payment is due upon completion of services unless other arrangements have been made. We accept cash, bank transfer, and major credit/debit cards. For custom builds, a deposit may be required before ordering components.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="terms-section">
          <h2 class="space-font" style="color: var(--aurora-green); font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px;">7. Uncollected Equipment</h2>
          <p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--starlight-white); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 20px;">
            Equipment not collected within 30 days of completion notification may be subject to storage charges. After 90 days, uncollected items may be disposed of at our discretion.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="terms-section">
          <h2 class="space-font" style="color: var(--aurora-green); font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px;">8. Contact Information</h2>
          <p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--starlight-white); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 20px;">
            For questions about these terms, please contact us at:
          </p>
          <div style="background: rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.1); border: 1px solid var(--plasma-cyan); border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px; margin-top: 12px;">
            <p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--starlight-white); font-size: 14px; margin: 0;">
              üìß david@chilterncomputers.net<br>
              üì± 07971 331814<br>
              üìç 38 Hilldene Avenue, Harold Hill, Romford, Essex, RM3 8YP
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 40px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid var(--plasma-cyan);">
          <a href="/contact" class="space-button">
            <span>üìû</span>
            Contact Us
          </a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>